* 2004年9月16日，[[卡姆航空|卡姆航空]]運營的一架[[安托諾夫An-24|安托諾夫An-24]]飛機在喀布爾降落時滑出跑道，機上27名乘客部分受輕傷，但飛機未受損。<ref>{{cite web|title=Crash of Antonov AN-24 at Kabul Airport (Afghanistan)|url=http://www.air-valid.co.uk/incidents/aeroport-de-kabul-afghanistan.html|publisher=Air-valid|accessdate=2015-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170804115608/http://www.air-valid.co.uk/incidents/aeroport-de-kabul-afghanistan.html|archive-date=2017-08-04|dead-url=yes}}{{en}}</ref>
